description: New to Market! 479 East 6th St, South Boston - a well-maintained multi-family in an unbeatable location, perfect for investors or owner-occupants. The first-floor unit features 1 bedroom and 1 full bath, while the spacious second-floor unit offers 2 bedrooms and 1.5 baths. Both apartments include hardwood floors throughout, updated kitchens with modern finishes, and renovated bathrooms. Ideally situated just blocks from the beach, parks, restaurants, and public transit, this property offers strong rental potential and long-term value in one of South Boston’s most sought-after neighborhoods.
